{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"4f7f6507edd4eceb","type":"group","x":-3640,"y":-3020,"width":5700,"height":2780,"color":"4","label":"The Kris Krises"},
		{"id":"1baa5f3a197de85c","type":"group","x":-3600,"y":-2960,"width":5620,"height":2160,"color":"3","label":"krisdreemurrkris"},
		{"id":"ca57fc9001860b76","type":"group","x":-1260,"y":-760,"width":1760,"height":500,"color":"3","label":"Kris D'vina"},
		{"id":"032c908ecc2b0664","type":"group","x":-1760,"y":-760,"width":450,"height":260,"color":"1","label":"Yes, There's Multiple"},
		{"id":"590b49b53bd54b06","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Kris' Birth.md","x":-400,"y":-735,"width":400,"height":443,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"9e879d06ff347355","type":"link","url":"https://mourningdew.phinarina.xyz/kris_dvina_kris/","x":-805,"y":-731,"width":365,"height":439},
		{"id":"658ace554eec80e4","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Media/Kris/Kris D'vina/Kris Sick.png","x":-1009,"y":-652,"width":164,"height":145,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"e11a876cd4ff3cab","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Media/Metacommunication/Discord Hints/Multiple Krises One.png","x":-1740,"y":-728,"width":400,"height":57,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"2457d1d6d96692c9","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Media/Kris/Kris D'vina/Kris Sick B.png","x":-1240,"y":-652,"width":177,"height":98,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"1e6c8dc4942df8bd","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Media/Metacommunication/Discord Hints/Multiple Krises Two.png","x":-1740,"y":-643,"width":400,"height":133,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"f93d53cd8f88775e","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Media/Metacommunication/Discord Hints/Oh, the poor children!.png","x":30,"y":-457,"width":398,"height":54,"color":"4"},
		{
			"id":"e5c1fe638191dfb1",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"'That night in the woods' can't have happened in a world where Dess was never lost. What does referring to it here mean??",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":29,
			"y":-378,
			"width":400,
			"height":86,
			"color":"1"
		},
		{
			"id":"113bbd93683bf04b",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"§ Suddenly, you\nthought very hard\nabout an animated\nseries you watched\nas a kid...\n§ \"Automatic Duck.\"",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-1860,
			"y":-2920,
			"width":260,
			"height":196,
			"color":"4"
		},
		{"id":"a9a866ebbf7bcc7c","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Canvases/Kris/Before The Story.canvas","portal":true,"x":-3560,"y":-2920,"width":1680,"height":2040},
		{
			"id":"5151e234265d369b",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"§ (You look into the fire...) \n§ (There's a strange machine in the fire, stripped of some of its parts.) \n§ (It looks like it's ancient.) \n§ (Some of the label is faded, but the letters you can make out say...) \n```\n§ (\"R     A        I   N        LLC\".)\n```\n§ (The logo...) \n§ (You put the machine back down.) \n\n§ Squeak! \n§ (...Underneath the machine was an automatic duck toy.) \n§ (It used to belong to you.) \n§ (Goodnight, sweet prince.) \n\n§ It's a smoldering pile of contraband.\n\n*(Kris' third channel description.)*",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-1560,
			"y":-2939,
			"width":560,
			"height":459,
			"color":"4"
		},
		{"id":"515d1db5d1f1856a","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Media/Kris/krisdreemurrkris/Kris Account.png","x":-1580,"y":-2020,"width":399,"height":82},
		{"id":"39072fe0f939818b","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Media/Kris/krisdreemurrkris/Kris' consultation screenshot (lq).png","x":-1140,"y":-2020,"width":400,"height":364},
		{"id":"464c0d71bd14601b","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Media/Kris/krisdreemurrkris/Can anyone try to recognize December.png","x":-1581,"y":-1900,"width":400,"height":91},
		{
			"id":"372f865e71172971",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"This is clearly one of the Krises narrating, and I'm FAIRLY sure it's Dreemurr in spite of the section sign usage due to it being at the lake.",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-690,
			"y":-2261,
			"width":360,
			"height":140,
			"color":"1"
		},
		{"id":"89b7808dd1b175dd","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Media/Kris/krisdreemurrkris/Important Person's Shirt A.png","x":-710,"y":-2020,"width":283,"height":400,"color":"4"},
		{
			"id":"b3654c65c5c0c62e",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"Clearly as capable of modifying the game for different answers as we are.",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-1070,
			"y":-1632,
			"width":260,
			"height":100,
			"color":"1"
		},
		{"id":"c9f75d6c6fab6d5a","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Media/Consultations/Round 1/Kris consultation A.png","x":-1563,"y":-1567,"width":360,"height":623},
		{
			"id":"5794380380c64dd9",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"Who is Kris referring to here?",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-370,
			"y":-2040,
			"width":260,
			"height":60,
			"color":"1"
		},
		{"id":"51936bfcb827ae16","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Media/Kris/Lake.png","x":-330,"y":-2590,"width":400,"height":300},
		{
			"id":"cdd97f21dcd7af7a",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"§ It’s just within reach. If you just wiggle your hand… \n§ …if you could only move your hand like so…",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-260,
			"y":-2251,
			"width":260,
			"height":120,
			"color":"4"
		},
		{
			"id":"c57de21c45f8e167",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"They, really are all happy, aren't they?\n\nYet, when I look at them... it's as if I dont even know who I'm looking at.\n\nI'll show them... that not all roads have to lead to the same place.\n\nThat there's another side, as long as you're able to go outside of the lines...\n\nSoon.\n\n\n\nhttps://www.youtube.com/@krisdreemurrkris",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-410,
			"y":-1892,
			"width":480,
			"height":335,
			"color":"4"
		},
		{"id":"89457a68dbf51514","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Media/Kris/krisdreemurrkris/Important Person's Shirt B.png","x":-682,"y":-1582,"width":226,"height":29,"color":"4"},
		{
			"id":"6901ca51ee43da5e",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"In reference to a 'Green Diamond' in someone's Consultation.",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-721,
			"y":-1463,
			"width":400,
			"height":60,
			"color":"1"
		},
		{"id":"3d1900dbef0db239","type":"file","file":"Conspiracy Board/Events/Media/Consultations/Round 2/Kris consultation B.png","x":-1186,"y":-1493,"width":441,"height":460},
		{"id":"33f900fc7a8d0819","type":"link","url":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vvHnpyFiO_k","x":-170,"y":-1412,"width":640,"height":360},
		{
			"id":"ff40d377e4df8c0e",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"About that last one... Don't you think something seems off...?",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":150,
			"y":-1692,
			"width":260,
			"height":100,
			"color":"4"
		},
		{
			"id":"bfdfcd8b4ce75220",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"*You don't like looking at this sort of thing.\n§ Wait, what was that *?\n                                                                -Kris \\[Blotched out with Black Ink\\]\n                                                                \n",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-721,
			"y":-1373,
			"width":530,
			"height":90,
			"color":"4"
		},
		{
			"id":"6d8fb99d379b2691",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"From one of the Excalidraw boards.",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-440,
			"y":-1263,
			"width":260,
			"height":72,
			"color":"1"
		},
		{
			"id":"c7bc4975dcff77f5",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"Playing up the fact they aren't exactly fond of themselves, here, with their consultation? Then again, not like I've heard of a Kris having a good experience with Therapy.",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":-1870,
			"y":-1243,
			"width":260,
			"height":200,
			"color":"1"
		},
		{
			"id":"97e71e7fd7fb6144",
			"type":"file",
			"file":"Conspiracy Board/Canvases/Kris/Kris' Timeline.canvas",
			"portal":true,
			"x":510,
			"y":-1752,
			"width":1480,
			"height":700,
			"interdimensionalEdges":[
				{
					"id":"03815c78b0b50456",
